data.description: Two Story home in a Quiet cul-de-sac. Great location to raise children and not worry about through traffic. This 2,600 living sq.ft. home has 4 bedrooms and a Loft upstairs,   with a 5th bedroom down stairs currently registered as an office/Bonus Room.. The large kitchen opens up to the family room with a fire place. The Laundry room is upstairs next to the loft. The master bedroom is over sized which includes a very roomy master bath which consists of a bath tub, double sinks, stand-uo shower, and very roomy walk-in closet. This property is a Must See !!
